@startuml
title Alipay+ Cashier Payment - End-to-End Flow
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam ArrowColor #4A5568
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #5B6B82
skinparam ActorBorderColor #5B6B82

legend right
|= Color |= System |
|<#FFF2CC>| User |
|<#D4F1EA>| Your Mobile App / Frontend |
|<#CFE2FF>| Your Backend / ACQP |
|<#FCE5CD>| Alipay+ Client / SDK / Checkout |
|<#F4CCCC>| Alipay+ Backend / Platform |
|<#E1D5E7>| MPP Wallet |
----
|<#2F80ED>| Blue arrows = Alipay+ SDK / checkout calls |
|<#C0392B>| Red arrows = Alipay+ backend API calls |
|<#4A5568>| Gray arrows = non-Alipay API / SDK steps |
endlegend

actor User #FFF2CC
participant "Your Mobile App / Web" as Client #D4F1EA
participant "Your Backend / ACQP" as ACQP #CFE2FF
participant "Alipay+ Checkout / SDK" as APC #FCE5CD
participant "Alipay+ Backend" as AP #F4CCCC
participant "MPP Wallet" as MPP #E1D5E7

autonumber "S00"

User -> Client: Place order
opt Render payment method
  Client -> ACQP: Request payment-method options
  ACQP -[#C0392B]> AP: consultPayment(order, env, settlement)
  AP -[#C0392B]--> ACQP: payment method list / promo / logo metadata
  ACQP --> Client: Renderable payment method data
end
User -> Client: Select Alipay+
Client -> ACQP: Create payment
ACQP -[#C0392B]> AP: pay(paymentRequestId,\npaymentNotifyUrl,\npaymentRedirectUrl,\npaymentMethodType=CONNECT_WALLET,\npresentmentMode=UNIFIED)
AP -[#C0392B]--> ACQP: resultStatus=U,\npaymentId,\nnormalUrl or paymentData
ACQP --> Client: Checkout payload
Client -[#2F80ED]> APC: Open normalUrl or SDK checkout
User -> APC: Choose wallet on checkout page
APC -> MPP: Redirect, deep link, or QR
User -> MPP: Authenticate and confirm payment
MPP --> APC: Final payment result
APC -[#2F80ED]--> AP: Final payment result
AP -[#C0392B]> ACQP: notifyPayment(success or fail)
ACQP -[#C0392B]--> AP: HTTP 200 + resultStatus=S

opt Callback missing or status still uncertain
  ACQP -[#C0392B]> AP: inquiryPayment(paymentRequestId or paymentId)
  AP -[#C0392B]--> ACQP: paymentResult S, F, or U
end

Client -> ACQP: Query order status
ACQP --> Client: Final order status
Client -> User: Show payment result page
@enduml
